description: Step into one of the most hilarious and heartwarming scenes from Zoom: Academy for Superheroes, where kids from across the country show up to audition for the ultimate honor—becoming the next generation of superheroes! 💥From invisibility mishaps to super strength that’s just a bit too strong, this tryout session is anything but ordinary.
